title: Baba's Falafel Food Truck
typeOfFood: Fast food, Mexican, Middle Eastern, Take-out only, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Mobile food truck that began service Oct 2012 as pure veg but no longer since it added lamb in spring 2013. Different flavors of falafel blending Arab with Mexican flavors, served in cones with some hummus. Check website for locations and times.
